\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 The true origins of Vampirism begin long before the planet Earth coalesced, in the moment when our universe exploded into being. In that moment, as vast quantities of magic spewed into our universe from dying reality that preceded it, the spirits were born. These spirits spread through our expanding universe, setting into motion the action of creation that would result in the formation of planets, stars, solar systems and galaxies. }
